OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA generally fair days weather
OL,6,Fin prospect with most places dry and
OL,7,Fbright. Sunny spells will turn
OL,8,Fincreasingly hazy from the west during
OL,9,Fthe afternoon. Winds light.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry start to the evening,
OL,12,Fbut turning increasingly cloudy with
OL,13,Fpatchy rain expected to spread across
OL,14,Ffrom the west during the rest of the
OL,15,Fnight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FCloudy with a few spots of
OL,18,Flight rain, but some brighter spells
OL,19,Fdeveloping in the afternoon. Outbreaks
OL,20,Fof rain will then spread northeast
OL,21,Fovernight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
