OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FShowery outbreaks of rain will be
OL,7,Finterspersed with some drier and
OL,8,Fbrighter conditions during this
OL,9,Fperiod. With winds staying
OL,10,Fsouthwesterly temperatures will be a
OL,11,Flittle up on the seasonal averages.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
